---
// FinalCTA.astro
---
<section class="py-32 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-secondary/20 blur-[150px] rounded-full z-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-secondary/20 blur-[120px] rounded-full z-0 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center bg-quaternary/40 border border-quaternary backdrop-blur-md p-12 md:p-20 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-theme-white tracking-tight mb-6">
      Digitaliza tu proceso de ventas inmobiliarias <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-theme-white to-secondary">hoy</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-secondary mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Tus asesores están perdiendo ventas por fricción en la información. Anticípate al mercado y transforma la experiencia de tus clientes, ahora mismo.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <a href="#demo" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-theme-white hover:bg-tertiary text-primary font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(255,255,255,0.25)] transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        Solicitar cotización
      </a>
      <a href="#showcase" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-quaternary hover:bg-tertiary hover:text-primary border border-quaternary text-theme-white font-medium text-lg rounded-xl transition-all">
        Ver ejemplo real
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-secondary">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">✓ Configuración rápida</div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">✓ Soporte especializado</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
